FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.kind_id  >  1 AND t.production_year  >  0 AND ci.person_id  <  509602 AND ci.role_id  =  8
